comments: Kennard (LAC) makes clean hand on ball contact to try and dislodge the ball from Gobert (UTA) in the post.

Morris Sr. (LAC) brings his arm down and makes clean contact to the ball with his forearm to dislodge it from Gobert (UTA) during his play at the basket. Any follow-through arm contact after the dislodge is deemed incidental.
George (LAC) disengages with O'Neale (UTA) to establish himself in Gobert's (UTA) path and absorb the contact on the screen.
O'Neale (UTA) reaches in and makes contact with George's (LAC) body, which affects his SQBR at the start of the drive.
Kennard (LAC) maintains a legal guarding position and absorbs the contact during the driving shot attempt by Mitchell (UTA).
As Bogdanovic (UTA) approaches the pick on the dribble hand-off, he makes incidental foot to foot contact with his teammate O'Neale (UTA) and the contact causes him to lose his balance.
Gobert (UTA) is in the paint for about three seconds when he is imminently exiting.
O'Neale (UTA) and Morris Sr. (LAC) engage and disengage and marginal contact occurs as they cut down the lane.

call_type: Turnover:  Out of Bounds - Bad Pass Turn
comments: Mitchell (UTA) throws an errant pass out of bounds.
Rondo (LAC) disengages from O'Neale (UTA) and makes clean ball contact to tip out the rebound.
Leonard (LAC) never establishes himself in Ingles' (UTA) path and delivers contact on the dribble hand-off, which affects his ability to defend.
Gobert (UTA) legally contests and cleanly blocks Morris Sr.'s (LAC) jump shot attempt.
